snippet.title: Kemono Friends: Kingdom - Official PV
snippet.description:
"Animal Girls, Befriend Today!"
Welcome to "Kingdom", an abandoned large-scale theme park where you will meet a diverse cast of animal friends and embark on a miraculous adventure with them!
